971
00:47:29,940 --> 00:47:31,260
They were so noisy.

972
00:47:31,699 --> 00:47:33,499
So, I retaliated.

973
00:47:33,659 --> 00:47:34,579
In the end,

974
00:47:34,699 --> 00:47:36,939
