977
00:47:40,460 --> 00:47:42,059
So annoying.

978
00:47:43,020 --> 00:47:44,939
Who's your future father-in-law?

979
00:47:46,580 --> 00:47:47,979
Are you serious?

980
00:47:48,940 --> 00:47:50,818
Are you going to forget about me

981
00:47:50,819 --> 00:47:52,220
